--
Please clarify the interaction between Applocker and Powershell.
The documentation implies that AppLocker can be used to *block* Powershell scripts.
In reality, Applocker only forces Powershell scripts to be run in Constrained Language Mode.

Please also clarify/document that in cases where a PS1 script is "blocked" AppLocker generates an 8007 event - which literally states the script will be blocked. After which the script runs.


